metatags.title: Left or Right?
metatags.og:description: These Left Twix vs. Right Twix commercials are annoyingly stupid. There is no Left and Right Twix. The packaging opens from the left and right, but the two pieces are Top and Bottom. And I don't think a candy bar company would ask: "Are you a Top or Bottom?" While the Twix assholes work their shit out. I'll be eating Kit Kat. Because it's not Left, Right, Top and Bottom. it's all one bar. Although their commercials are wrong, too. I never break off a piece of a Kit Kat bar for anybody. I just give them their own bar.
